title: Dm2 Mixman Mixer - Additional Software to convert to a MIDI cont
description:
These are all the additional files to allow you to make your Mixman DM2 into a MIDI controller, suitable for controlling Traktor or Virtual DJ.

Contents:

> MIDIYoke
> DM2MIDI V1.0
> DM2MIDI V1.1
> The Mixman DM2 manual (PDF)
> Additional files and Config information for Traktor and Virtual DJ
